{"tid":2495641,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"HKFP：港府向美國游說公司支付8,400萬 聘美前議員就《香港人權與民主法案》作游說","createTime":"2021-04-19T10:00:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T10:24:28.000Z","uid":301533,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d244a97a292c563dbc17f58c3ef018ec1b9adce0","tid":2495641,"uid":301533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:00:10.000Z","msg":"美國國會於去年11月通過《香港人權與民主法案》（下稱《法案》）．網媒HKFP調查發現，港府在2014至2020年期間，透過香港貿易發展局，向美國的游說公司支付至少8,400萬港元，聘用包括前美國國會議員的說客進行「政治活動」，及安排與美國政客會面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210419/5I2P5PC6RJBBND2TPWV6H6WWEE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210419%2F5I2P5PC6RJBBND2TPWV6H6WWEE&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx2a%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=da475943\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210419%2F5I2P5PC6RJBBND2TPWV6H6WWEE&h=fd39db0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210419/5I2P5PC6RJBBND2TPWV6H6WWEE</a>"},{"pid":"00999b225e629015d6dc3dd2178d489d61c07373","tid":2495641,"uid":124439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:01:19.000Z","msg":"係咪咁天真呀"},{"pid":"947df21f0521b3607dc6de57229ba7c06f425b2e","tid":2495641,"uid":83582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:02:19.000Z","msg":"咁都唔算勾結外國勢力?"},{"pid":"ba0288e45991a5e89626e6d8da2cb83f35b64494","tid":2495641,"uid":218082,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:02:19.000Z","msg":"美國游說公司:fatfat,反正點做都游說唔到但錢照袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw間公司幫恐怖份子做嘢唔驚俾人制裁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a8e38d2ca92b3b733483168ab27fffa51de61b","tid":2495641,"uid":3086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite